name: meditative
description: anacam webcam photos. anacam was a 12 year long performance art piece that achieved international attention and acclaim. shown in galleries such as MoMO. i lived my life on webcam from 1997- 2009. so you are buyinng a piece of internet history. this was before google or aol or any of that. 7 million people would watch all i pointed my webcam at as well as many writings. there is a lot out there about me on the internet such as books as and dissertations but most have not understoof what my webcam was actually about. people saw what what they wanted. my conclusion is that it was a giant ink blot.
